OL,3,CChronic illness poses 'almost
OL,4,Cunquantifiable' challenge for Welsh NHS
OL,6,FChronic health conditions pose an
OL,7,F"extraordinary, almost unquantifiable"
OL,8,Fchallenge for the health experts have
OL,9,Fwarned.
OL,11,FIt is estimated that 48% of people in
OL,12,FWales are living with a chronic or
OL,13,Flong-term condition, with 19%
OL,14,Fexperiencing two or more.
OL,16,FBut an ongoing Senedd inquiry into how
OL,17,Fwell people with such conditions are
OL,18,Fsupported has found that number is
OL,19,Flikely to increase, with more person-
OL,20,Fcentred care needed.
