OL,6,FA chronic condition is a health
OL,7,Fcondition or disease that is
OL,8,Fpersistent, severe or otherwise long-
OL,9,Flasting in its effects.
OL,11,FTracy Cross, from , was diagnosed with
OL,12,FCOPD and asthma after doctors
OL,13,Finitially put her breathlessness,
OL,14,Fwhich began after giving birth to her
OL,15,Ffourth child, down to depression.
OL,17,F"I was getting frustrated with myself,
OL,18,Fgetting upset," she said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
