OL,6,F"They told me that the breathlessness
OL,7,Fwas down to me being upset and
OL,8,Fdepression and I said, 'no there's
OL,9,Fmore to it than that, I know there is'.
OL,11,F"It just made me feel really horrible.
OL,12,FI couldn't do much, I had other
OL,13,Fchildren to look after at the time too
OL,14,Fand it was getting me down but I swore
OL,15,Fit wasn't down to the depression."
OL,17,FTracy was eventually put on a six-week
OL,18,Fpulmonary rehabilitation programme,
OL,19,Fwhich provided her with breathing
OL,20,Fexercises and advice on how to manage
OL,21,Fher condition.
