OL,6,FShe said the programme "dramatically"
OL,7,Fchanged her life.
OL,9,F"I couldn't walk from the waiting room
OL,10,Fto the doctor's office without feeling
OL,11,Fbreathless. I've gone from that to
OL,12,Fdoing a 5K (walk), now a 10K.
OL,14,F"Had I not had that and learnt about
OL,15,Fit I probably wouldn't be here now."
OL,17,FBut Tracy, who works closely with the
OL,18,Fcharity Asthma and Lung UK, said
OL,19,Faccess to pulmonary rehabilitation is
OL,20,F"patchy" across Wales.
