OL,6,FDad-of-two Thomas Leahy, who lives in
OL,7,FBarry, was diagnosed with relapsing
OL,8,Fremitting multiple sclerosis in 2022
OL,9,Fafter multiple hospital visits.
OL,11,FThe university lecturer initially paid
OL,12,Fprivately for treatment to avoid a
OL,13,F"massive" NHS waiting list, but is now
OL,14,Funder NHS care.
OL,16,FHe said some people with chronic
OL,17,Fconditions are being left "in the
OL,18,Fwilderness".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
