OL,3,CChronic illness poses 'almost
OL,4,Cunquantifiable' challenge for Welsh NHS
OL,6,F"You just feel like in a sense you've
OL,7,Fdropped out of society and society's
OL,8,Fforgotten about you, and you're just
OL,9,Fstuck in limbo of pain.
OL,11,F"For me, what governments need to do
OL,12,Fis provide people with opportunities
OL,13,Fto achieve their best alongside that
OL,14,Fchronic condition.
OL,16,F"That allows people to contribute to
OL,17,Fsociety, economy, education, etc. So
OL,18,Fit makes no sense to have a system
OL,19,Fwhere people are being delayed doing
OL,20,Fthat."
