OL,6,Fhealth economist Pippa Anderson said
OL,7,Fchronic illness is "an extraordinary,
OL,8,Falmost unquantifiable challenge" for
OL,9,Fthe health service.
OL,11,F"One of the big drivers of course is
OL,12,Fthat we're all living longer and as
OL,13,Fyou live longer you can accumulate
OL,14,Fproblems that can be managed by the
OL,15,Fhealth service.
OL,17,F"It has a huge financial impact
OL,18,Fbecause you have to pay for more
OL,19,Fhealth professionals, more drugs, more
OL,20,Finfrastructure.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
