OL,3,CChronic illness poses 'almost
OL,4,Cunquantifiable' challenge for Welsh NHS
OL,6,F"Politically it's not so easy to get
OL,7,Fgood vibes from your voters if you put
OL,8,Fin interventions that pay off way down
OL,9,Fthe line.
OL,11,F"If you put in interventions early
OL,12,Fyou'll get the benefits 40-50 years
OL,13,Fdown the line, whereas trying to deal
OL,14,Fwith the crisis now by throwing money
OL,15,Fat the problem isn't very helpful.
OL,16,FIt's a very difficult situation for
OL,17,Fany government."
