OL,6,FRussell George MS, chair of the
OL,7,FSenedd's Health and Social Care
OL,8,FCommittee, said the inquiry into
OL,9,Fchronic conditions has seen some
OL,10,F"emerging themes".
OL,12,F"We know that there are more people
OL,13,Fnow living with chronic conditions and
OL,14,Fmultiple conditions and it's predicted
OL,15,Fthat that's only going to increase."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
