OL,3,CChronic illness poses 'almost
OL,4,Cunquantifiable' challenge for Welsh NHS
OL,6,F"We can see there's a need for person-
OL,7,Fcentred care, and by that I mean the
OL,8,Fperson being at the centre of decision-
OL,9,Fmaking. Where they may have multiple
OL,10,Fchronic conditions, services should be
OL,11,Fwrapped around them rather than looked
OL,12,Fat in isolation.
OL,14,F"We found that those living in more
OL,15,Fdeprived areas are more likely to have
OL,16,Fmultiple conditions and poorer health
OL,17,Foutcomes as well."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
