OL,6,FThe Welsh Government said it will
OL,7,Frespond to the inquiry "in due
OL,8,Fcourse", with the Health Minister due
OL,9,Fto appear before the inquiry next
OL,10,Fmonth.
OL,12,FIt also said it expects health boards
OL,13,Fto provide the support and care people
OL,14,Fwith chronic conditions need.
